<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.trougnouf.Cfait</id>
  <name>Cfait</name>
  <summary>Powerful, fast and elegant CalDAV task manager</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0-only</project_license>
  <developer id="com.trougnouf">
    <name>Benoit Brummer (Trougnouf)</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>
      Cfait is designed for speed and stability using Rust. It puts you in control of your data with a local-first approach that syncs seamlessly across your devices via CalDAV.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li
            >Syncs Everywhere: Compatible with Nextcloud, iCloud, Radicale, and other standard CalDAV servers.</li>
      <li
            >Offline First: Optimistic UI updates mean you never wait for a server response.</li>
      <li
            >Smart Input: Typing "Buy cat food !1 @tomorrow" automatically sets priority and due date.</li>
      <li>Productivity: GTD Workflow, Sub-tasks, Dependencies, and Tags.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

